There is measurement point for the 6 inner ESCSs.
There coordinates in the conic CS are given in polar coordinates by
\begin{eqnarray}
  \label{eq:64}
  \rho &=& [[L]] - \rho_0, \\
  \theta &=& -\pi{2k+3\over 6},
\end{eqnarray}
where $\rho_0$ is the root of
\begin{equation}
  \label{eq:65}
  [[D_full]]^2 - ([[D_assembly/2]]-\rho_0)^2 - \left[ F([[D_assembly/2]]) - F(\rho_0) \right]^2 = 0,
\end{equation}
and with
\begin{equation}
  \label{eq:66}
  F(r) = {c r^2 \over 1 + \sqrt{1-\kappa(cr)^2} } .
\end{equation}

There are 2 measurement points for the 6 outer ESCSs.
The polar coordinates in the conic CS are given by
\begin{eqnarray}
  \label{eq:67}
  \rho &=& [[D_full]]/2, \\
  \theta &=& -\pi{2k+1\over 6},  
\end{eqnarray}
and
\begin{eqnarray}
  \label{eq:68}
  \rho &=& [[D_full]]/2, \\
  \theta &=& \pi{7-2k\over 6}.
\end{eqnarray}

